RB2AUD.original: ~z~Johnny and Tuna are sleeping with the fishes, Ray. I'm sorry.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~Johnny和Tuna都要去河底喂鱼了，Ray。我很抱歉。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~I'm fucking coming down, asshole. I feel like death.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~老娘要撑不住了，混蛋。感觉跟要死了一样。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~I sure hope we ain't lost any on the route. Things got shaken up pretty good back there.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~希望我们没在路上掉过钻石，刚才震得可厉害了。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Shit, can't you learn to play nice, Nicky?
~z~Ah hell, Nicky. They was good earners. You gotta control yourself, you're a fucking maniac.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，Nicky。他俩很能干的。学会控制自己，你这个疯子。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Me and Luca didn't get on so well, Ray. This thing ain't happening.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~我和Luca相处得不好，Ray。计划失败了。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~You think that's funny? Shit. You're an imbecile. We gotta talk about this.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~这很有趣吗？操，你这个白痴。我们得好好谈谈了。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Jimmy Pegorino is a personal friend of mine,
~z~Alright, Nicky. What's done is done. Come see me.
~z~We don't want none of those bags to break, Nicky.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~我们不希望任何一袋垃圾破掉，Nicky。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~This truck can't drive itself. Get back in.
~z~Fuck, I thought this was going to be easy. Why does everything have to get complicated?
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~操，我还以为会很容易。怎么做什么最后都一团糟？

RB2AUD.original: ~z~You ain't making this easy on us.
~z~-Can I get a Goddamn coffee here?~n~-Yeah, you look like you could really use some Goddamn caffeine.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~－能他妈给老娘上杯咖啡吗？~n~－确实，你看上去确实得他妈来点咖啡因。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Luca and Johnny are on ice, Ray. Shit happens.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~Luca和Johnny都进冷柜了，Ray。发生了很多事。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~I ain't gonna get caught by the cops with this stolen ice. Lose 'em before we pick it up.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~我可不想带着赃物钻石被警察抓到。在我们收回钻石前甩了他们。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Me and your crew didn't get on so good, Ray.
~z~Nah, me and Tuna will look after them. Sort them out from the trash.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~不了，我和Tuna会处理的。把钻石从垃圾里分出来。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~We was saying that there's a lot of opportunities for this to go wrong. The bag could split.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~我们在说这个计划很容易出问题。垃圾袋会破掉。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~The whole crew? Va fanabla! Come back to Drusilla's.
~z~There's no time for this shit, get back into the truck, Nicky.
~z~Go over to F between Columbus and Denver, there'll be a truck waiting there.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~去Columbus大道和Denver大道之间的F路，那里有辆垃圾车等着。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~I make the call on who gets whacked, tough guy. We gotta have a meeting.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~杀谁我说了算，硬汉，我们会见面的。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~We're just trying to pick up the damn trash.
~z~Really? I wanted to be an astronaut when I was growing up, not a gangster.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~是吗？我小时候想当太空人，而不是混黑道。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~We can't collect this ice with the cops on us. Lose the heat.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~被条子追的时候没法钻石，甩了他们。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~The diamonds could go missing real easy.
~z~That's life, my friend. Nothing works out the way you want it to.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~这就是生活，我的朋友。没一件事能顺你心意。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~-Garbage with a lot of ice in it.~n~-Today?
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~－里面有很多钻石的垃圾。~n~－能快点吗？

RB2AUD.original: ~z~I dunno. These diamonds is serious. Anyone who heard of 'em would want them.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~我也不知道，这些钻石很值钱。谁听说了都想来截胡。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Didn't think I'd be muscle for the mob neither.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~也没想到自己会成为黑帮的打手。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Something smelled fishy about Tuna, Ray. He's not around no more.
~z~And if there's a man who knows how to get angry, it's Ray. Later.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~如果有一个人很容易生气，那便是Ray。回见。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~That's why we're going to be extra careful, right? We wouldn't want that to happen, would we?
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~所以才要格外小心，对吧？我们也不想出什么岔子，对吧？

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah... you wanted a career in waste disposal, now you got one.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~对...你不是想要垃圾场的工作吗，现在你有了。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~This is the other one, Tuna. Grab it.
~z~That's why you gotta take the opportunities you can when they're right in front of you.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~所以才要及时抓住眼前的机遇。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~You could say that. Ray got that tweaker chick of his, the biker broad, you met her?
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~可以这么说吧。Ray的那个吸毒女友，飞车党的，你见过吗？

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Ray, man. That Johnny kid got put out with the trash. I'm sorry.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~Ray，伙计。Johnny已经死在垃圾堆里了，我很抱歉。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~How'd they find us? I thought that we went to all this trouble so no one would know?
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~怎么被发现了？我们特意绕这么大个圈子还被发觉了？

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Fuck me, Nicky. I had some hopes for that cugine. Come see me.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~我操，Nicky。我还有点期待那个老兄的。过来见我。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Three guys, good guys, friends of mine.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~有三个人，三个好人，都是我的朋友。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~You keep an eye on them? They didn't pull nothing?
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~你有盯着他们吗？他们没私吞吧？

RB2AUD.original: ~z~I sorta get that, but I ain't happy. Let's have a meet.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~我明白了，但是我不开心。让我们见个面。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~That a fact? Being a space monkey would probably pay better than this work.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~真这么想？当太空猴的工资可能是比这个工作高。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Alright, Nicky. What's done is done. Come see me.
~z~So, you took care of that thing.
~z~So, someone's been throwing out a load of diamonds?
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~合着有人扔掉了一大堆钻石？

RB2AUD.original: ~z~We've taken this ice off a the guy that owns the place.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~钻石就是从这家店的老板那儿弄来的。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Ray came up with this plan to keep a bit of distance between us and the robbery.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~Ray的这个计划就是为了避免我们和抢钻石间产生直接联系。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Don't let these mooks take our diamonds.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~别让这些白痴抢走我们的钻石。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~I can't see that we got much opportunity here. Either we lose these shitheads or we're screwed.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~我是看不出现在有什么机遇。甩不掉这些猪头就完了。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~No wonder everyone's turning state's when the wages is like this.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~就这么点酬劳，也难怪一个个都会去自首坦白。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Every immigrant's dream ain't it? Being a wiseguy I mean, not trash collecting.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~移民都这么幻想，不是吗？要做聪明人，不去收垃圾。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~First pickup's in Chinatown. Let's hit it.
~z~Luca and Johnny are on ice, Ray. Shit happens.
~z~I look after my friends... I got a lot of friends. Important friends.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~我很关照我的朋友...我有很多朋友。很重要的朋友。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Ray got her to get her friends to steal the ice off of some club owner guy.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~Ray让她和她的朋友从一个夜店老板地方偷走了那些钻石。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~You just gonna have to do your best. Ain't ya? We're not losing this ice.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~你尽力而为就行。我们不会放弃钻石的。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~The bikers is taking the heat for this shit.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~这事的黑锅现在在飞车党身上。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Defend that ice like it's your cunt.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~把那钻石当你的命根子护着。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Well, don't try your luck at the door any time soon and if you do, don't tip the bouncer with a diamond.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~以后别去那边乱转。就算真去了，别把钻石当给守门人的小费。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Good drivin', Nicky. I thought I was gonna be checking out for sure.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~好车技，Nicky。我刚才还以为自己死定了。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~This is it. You got us here, Nicky.
~z~This ain't the easiest way to pick this shit up, even if we don't want to attract any attention.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~就算不想引起别人注意，也有更简单的方法能拿回钻石吧。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Can I get a Goddamned coffee over here?
~z~So, Luca, you are a professional trash collector when you ain't working for Ray?
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~那个，Luca，你不替Ray干活的时候就是专业收垃圾的吗？

RB2AUD.original: ~z~The manager of one of his waste depots was holding out on profits a couple a years back.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~几年前他的一个垃圾站的经理偷偷拿了一点回扣，

RB2AUD.original: ~z~I dunno what this crew's gonna do without Luca. I looked to him, you know. For, like, leadership and shit.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~我不知道没了Luca这个小队还怎么行动。我听他的，你知道吗。因为，他，有领导力这样的东西。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~When I arrived in Liberty City, I didn't imagine that I'd become a trash collector.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~来到自由城的时候，我没想到自己会成为收垃圾的。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, they got it. They... they left it where you said.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~好，已经弄到了。他们把钻石放到你要求的地方了。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~We ain't doing too good back here.
~z~I'm not having Ray cut my balls off because you don't think this truck's fast enough.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~我可不想因为你嫌弃这车不够快就被Ray给阉了。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Course not. You know how pissed Ray would get if he found out some diamonds were missin'.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~当然不想。你也知道要是漏了钻石，Ray会有多生气。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~This guy who owns some big clubs in the city. You heard of a place called Maisonette 9?
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~在城里开了好几家大型夜店的家伙。听说过9号豪宅吗？

RB2AUD.original: ~z~You seem real at home in this truck.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~你上垃圾车就跟回了家一样。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~I think I worked with a member of that gang up on Bohan. He was called Johnny or eh, something.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~我记得我和那个帮会的人在Bohan合作过。他好像叫Johnny来着。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~You want me take the ice to Ray then?
~z~That mook ain't gonna be following us no more. Let's get the ice back. You've done good, Nicky.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~这些呆子没法再跟着我们了。把钻石带回去吧。你做得很好，Nicky。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~I think you should worry about Ray and those diamonds before anything else. I'll see you around, Tuna.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~我觉得你还是先担心Ray和那些钻石比较好。我们回头见，Tuna。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Well that job got screwed up, didn't it?
~z~Shit, man. Looks like we got company.
~z~It's because I care... you know that.
~z~Nothing... I haven't been to bed yet.
~z~Alright, Tuna, John Boy, you got the threads. Get on the back and get the trash.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~好了，Tuna，小强，工作服你们都有了。到后面去负责收垃圾。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Her friends are the Lost biker gang.
~z~Who'd these diamonds belong to before us?
~z~I ain't surprised we got a bit of attention.
~z~Yeah, me and Tuna was saying that before yous got here.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~对，你来之前我和Tuna就在聊这个。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Luca and his crew have got the stuff, Ray. It's all in the back of the truck.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~Luca和他的人拿到货了，Ray。都在垃圾车后面装着。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~They ain't on us no more. Good driving. Now all's you got to do is bring the ice home safe.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~甩掉他们了，好车技。现在只要把钻石安全带回家就行。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~My God, you look like shit. What's wrong?
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~天哪，你看上去不太好，怎么了?

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Your buddies are turning state's because they're too pussy to do their time.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~你的人会投案坦白，纯粹是因为不敢蹲号子。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Are you busting my balls, Nicky? What the fuck?
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~你这是看不起我吗，Nicky？你丫想啥呢？

RB2AUD.original: ~z~then the pop of his skull goin'. I nearly lost my lunch.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~再然后就是头骨碎裂。我差点把午饭吐出来。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Fuck me, Nicky. I had some hopes for that cugine. Come see me.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~我操，Nicky。我还有点期待那个老兄的。过来见我。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~This truck is not really going to outrun anybody, is it?
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~这卡车谁都甩不掉吧，是不是？

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Ah... Niko, I need you to go collect some garbage for me.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~啊...Niko，我需要你去帮我收一些垃圾。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~You think I'd take the trash out every day, like some fuckin' mook?
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~你以为我会跟个白痴一样每天倒垃圾？

RB2AUD.original: ~z~White trash motherfucker. What is wrong with you?
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~狗娘养的白皮垃圾，你有什么毛病？

RB2AUD.original: ~z~They'd rather have plastic surgery and a life sentence in suburban hell than take their punishment like real men.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~他们宁愿做整容手术，到鸟不拉屎的乡下度过余生，也不愿意像男子汉一样接受刑罚。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~I don't know, Ray. You don't trust them, then weigh the ice. Catch you round.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~我不知道，Ray。信不过他们就自己去称。回见。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Alright, Nicky. What's done is done. Come see me.
~z~Shit, try to kill people who ain't good earners. Let's you and me have a sit down.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~操，就不能找个废物下手吗。之后我们再谈谈。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~I didn't say it was impossible. It's just going to be difficult.
~z~I guess that anyone involved in this thing of ours
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~或许跟我们这件事有关的人

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, but you got to admit the money we're getting ain't shit. We bust our balls and for what?
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~确实，但我们的报酬真的太少了。费这么大劲都是为了什么啊？

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Hey, Ray. I'm sorry but I had to put Luca and Tuna down. I didn't trust them.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，Ray。很抱歉，我把Luca和Tuna干掉了。我不信他们。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~This is Tunafish and Johnny Spaz. Tuna, Johnny, Niko.
~z~Ray, I hate to tell you this but your friend Tuna is sleeping with the fishes.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~Ray，很遗憾地告诉你，你的朋友Tuna现在要到河底喂鱼去了。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Ray, the job did not go to plan. We lost Luca and Tuna. I'm sorry.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~Ray，事情没能按计划进行。我们失去了Luca和Tuna。我很抱歉。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Ray fed him to a dump truck.
~z~Can you open up the back, Nicky?
~z~Nice driving, Nicky. Looks like you lost 'em. Let's bring this ice home.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~车技不错，Nicky。看来你甩掉他们了，把钻石送回家吧。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Tuna, this is it. Grab the bag.
~z~Money ain't the only thing I'm looking for in Liberty City, Luca. I'll take what Ray gives me.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~钱不是我在自由城的唯一目标，Luca。Ray给我多少钱都行。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~is in the waste management business but it ain't usually this hands on, you know?
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~都有参与垃圾处理事业，但也不是靠这个吃饭的，懂吗？

RB2AUD.original: ~z~I don't think we going to complete our round, Ray. The truck's trashed.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~我觉得我们没法完成任务了，Ray。垃圾车成垃圾了。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Too bad about the truck. I guess Ray's gonna be pissed.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~卡车的情况真是太糟了。我想Ray会气炸的。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~It sure fucking did. I got a feeling that Ray'll care more about not getting the diamonds though.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~当然搞砸了。不过我觉得Ray会更在意我们没弄到钻石就是了。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Next one's on H street. Move out, Nicky.
~z~Did these bikers get so fucked on meth that they threw the ice away?
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~这些飞车党是吸冰毒吸坏脑子才把这些钻石给扔了？

RB2AUD.original: ~z~There was this point where the sounds of his screams stopped and all you could hear was his bones crushin',
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~一段时间后他的尖叫停了，传来的只剩下骨头粉碎的声音，

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Nah. It seems the club owner's got more connections than a subway line.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~不是，那个夜店老板的人际关系似乎比铁路还复杂。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Gimme a break, okay? I feel like death.
~z~Yeah, you still get your hands dirty though. Who'd these diamonds belong to before us?
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~懂了，但你手上还是不太干净。这些钻石原来的主人是谁？

RB2AUD.original: ~z~You should start looking for a new crew, Ray. The old one's in a better place.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~你需要找新的手下了, Ray。老的几个上天堂了。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~This is important work I got for ya. Come back and see me.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~这次的活很重要的。再回来找我。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Fuck me, Nicky. I had some hopes for that cugine. Come see me.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~干，Nicky。我从表兄那听到一些消息。过来见我。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~He's in with the Ancelottis, the Dominicans up in Northwood, everybody.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~他和Ancelotti家族有关，和Northwood的多米尼加人有关，谁都跟他有关。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~You gotta stop me smoking this stuff, Ray.
~z~They sure did, Luca. Here's hopin' we can find 'em all.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~是很厉害，Luca。希望钻石一颗都没少。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Get rid of the cops, Nicky. We don't want the feds seeing us collect this ice.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~甩掉条子，Nicky。我们不希望被警察发现我们带着钻石。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~Crap, someone's got wise to us. Let's get the hell outta here. Drive to Fishmarket South.
RB2AUD.translated: ~z~靠，有人发现我们了。快他妈离开这儿，去鱼市南。

RB2AUD.original: ~z~He ain't gonna be happy, Nicky. That's for damn sure.
